00:11:24,476 --> 00:11:26,811
I'm of an age now,
we become nostalgic,

292
00:11:26,853 --> 00:11:30,357
we become philosophical.

293
00:11:30,398 --> 00:11:33,589
One can, if a successful gentleman
of many accomplishments,

294
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:36,737
for instance, with a little
bit of money to spend,

295
00:11:36,779 --> 00:11:39,595
make, as Emerson
advised, your own world

296
00:11:39,596 --> 00:11:40,908
far from the madness.

