00:12:00,803 --> 00:12:03,473
As young cooks, looking
at his incredible rise

305
00:12:03,515 --> 00:12:05,684
from working-class
boy to the youngest

306
00:12:05,685 --> 00:12:08,936
three-Michelin-starred chef in
the world, we were inspired,

307
00:12:08,978 --> 00:12:11,481
not just by his
accomplishments and his food,

308
00:12:11,523 --> 00:12:14,296
which were amazing, no
great chef had ever

309
00:12:14,297 --> 00:12:17,028
looked like him before
or talked like him.

310
00:12:17,070 --> 00:12:19,573
We were not, it appeared, alone.

311
00:12:19,614 --> 00:12:22,867
I want to turn Rudloe into a house...
