00:14:46,052 --> 00:14:48,429
The flip side of that coin...

370
00:14:50,598 --> 00:14:52,058
was nature.

371
00:14:53,267 --> 00:14:57,480
It was all those beautiful
ingredients, that beautiful

372
00:14:57,481 --> 00:14:58,981
contradiction.

